## Rounding  
Some important functions we apply on numerical values  

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- 9/4
floor(x)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```{.custom-output}
[1] 2
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
ceiling(x)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```{.custom-output}
[1] 3
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
round(x)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
