5          5  40 118.0 67.66667
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# Replace NAs with median (better for skewed data)
clinical_data$age[is.na(clinical_data$age)] <- median(clinical_data$age, na.rm = TRUE)
clinical_data
```

